      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. I have one specific case where an employee is constantly disrupting the team dynamic—like they're just being difficult or causing unnecessary friction for no reason. If I wanted to describe that kind of \"troublesome\" behavior in a review without sounding personal or aggressive, what kind of phrasing would work best?",
