      "role": "user",
      "content": "Okay, I see. So I should focus on the impact. But it's tricky because it really feels like they're just being a bit of a nuisance or acting out in a very erratic/mischievous way. Is there any way to describe someone who is basically just a constant, unpredictable source of trouble or chaos in the office without it sounding like a character assassination?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
