      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "If the behavior is erratic and unpredictable, focus on consistency and process rather than labeling it as \"mischievous.\" You might use language such as, \"Requires greater consistency in approach to project timelines\" or \"Opportunities exist to maintain a more predictable workflow within team settings.\" This frames the issue as a lack of reliable execution rather than a personality flaw.",
      "source": "target",
